Jet Engines Market Report
Jet Engines Market Overview
The global jet engines market was valued at approximately $87 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach $128 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.6% during the forecast period. The market encompasses commercial, military, and general aviation segments, each driven by advancements in engine technology, increasing demand for fuel efficiency, and surging air traffic globally. Technological innovations, such as hybrid-electric propulsion systems, are reshaping the market, enhancing performance, and reducing carbon emissions.

